Exercise 2

beyonce_sum_e2 <- beyonce_sum_e1 |> slice(1:20) |>
  mutate(word = as.factor(word)) |>
  mutate(word = fct_reorder(word, n))

ggplot(data = beyonce_sum_e2, aes(x = word, y = n)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_segment(aes(xend = word, yend = 0)) +
  coord_flip() +
  theme_minimal()
